  "description": {
    "en-US": "Travel phrases for Italy with audio, built for Trenitalia and Italo trains, hotel arrivals, coffee bars, restaurant ordering, and everyday travel logistics.",
    "zh-CN": "意大利旅行短语卡，围绕 Trenitalia 和 Italo 火车、酒店入住、咖啡吧、餐厅点单和日常出行沟通整理。"
  },
  "intro": {
    "en-US": "Built for Italy trips where train platforms, hotel check-ins, espresso bars, museum slots, and dinner reservations all stack up quickly. These cards are most useful when you need short Italian for binario changes, coffee-bar etiquette, or the small restaurant details that are easy to miss in translation.",
    "zh-CN": "这套意大利短语适合那种火车站站台、酒店入住、咖啡吧、博物馆预约和晚餐预订会连续出现的旅行节奏。遇到要确认 binario、应对咖啡吧礼节，或说明餐厅里那些容易被忽略的小细节时，短语卡会非常实用。"
  },
  "teaser": {
    "en-US": "Built for Italy train travel, coffee bars, restaurant etiquette, hotel arrivals, and quick museum-day logistics.",
    "zh-CN": "适合意大利火车出行、咖啡吧、餐厅礼节、酒店入住和博物馆日程沟通。"
  },
  "travelTips": {
    "en-US": [
      "Keep transport phrases ready for Trenitalia or Italo counters, binario changes, and coach numbers before a long train day.",
      "Dining phrases matter because coperto, table service timing, and bill requests can work differently from what travelers expect.",
      "Coffee bars move fast, so a short request for espresso, takeaway, or the receipt is easier when you can show or say it quickly."
    ],
    "zh-CN": [
      "如果当天要坐 Trenitalia 或 Italo，最好先备好站台变更、车厢号和柜台询问相关短语。",
      "意大利餐厅里 coperto、上菜节奏和要账单的方式都和很多游客习惯不同，所以餐饮短语特别值得先看。",
      "咖啡吧节奏很快，想点 espresso、外带，或索要小票时，能快速说出或展示短语会轻松很多。"
    ]
  },
  "highlights": {
    "en-US": [
      "Trains, coperto, and coffee bar etiquette",
      "Hotels, museums, and reservations",
      "Food allergies, takeaway, and receipts"
    ],
    "zh-CN": [
      "火车、coperto 与咖啡吧礼节",
      "酒店、博物馆与预约沟通",
      "过敏说明、外带与小票"
    ]
  },
